donk.
donk。

2
00:00:07,666 --> 00:00:11,566
You were typing at the beginning of the game to your teammates.
你比赛一开始就在给队友打字。

3
00:00:11,666 --> 00:00:13,733
You said you wanted to make them cry.
你说你想把对面打哭。

4
00:00:14,166 --> 00:00:18,000
I don't think they're crying right now,
but they're definitely sad and unhappy.
我不觉得他们现在真的哭了，
但肯定已经很难受了。

5
00:00:18,366 --> 00:00:25,200
How much did this win mean to you?
Because it sounds to me like it's different from what you normally say.
这场胜利对你来说意味着什么？
因为这话听起来，确实不太像你平时会说的。

6
00:00:26,333 --> 00:00:31,366
It's great. It's a good start,
I mean, a great sign in front of the Major.
感觉很棒。
这是个很好的开始，也是 Major 前一个很棒的信号。

7
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:36,800
And it's great to win this way,
in this arena, in front of this crowd.
而且能用这样的方式赢下来，
还是在这个场馆、在这么多观众面前，感觉更棒。

